{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"IDBEnvironment","mdn_url":"/ja/docs/Web/API/IDBEnvironment","locale":"ja","native":"日本語","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/IDBEnvironment\"><code>IDBEnvironment</code></a></strong></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>\n\n<div class=\"warning notecard\" id=\"sect1\">\n<p><strong>Important</strong>: As of Firefox 52, the property defined in this mixin has been moved to the <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/WindowOrWorkerGlobalScope\"><code>WindowOrWorkerGlobalScope</code></a> mixin, and other browsers will follow suit. Look to that page for up-to-date details.</p>\n</div>\n\n<p><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/IndexedDB_API\">IndexedDB API</a>&nbsp;の&nbsp;<strong><code>IDBEnvironment</code></strong>&nbsp;インタフェースには、IndexedDB の機能へアクセスするための&nbsp;<code>indexedDB</code>&nbsp;プロパティがあります。これは、<a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Window\"><code>window</code></a>&nbsp;と&nbsp;<a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Worker\"><code>Worker</code></a>オブジェクトによって実装された、最上位の IndexedDB インタフェースです。</p>\n\n<p></p><div class=\"notecard note\" id=\"sect2\">\n  <p><strong>注:</strong> この機能は <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Web_Workers_API\">Web Worker</a> 内で利用可能です</p>\n</div><p></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"プロパティ","title":"プロパティ","isH3":false,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"idbenvironment.indexeddb_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/indexedDB\"><code>IDBEnvironment.indexedDB</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> <span title=\"This value may not be changed.\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">読取専用 </span></dt>\n <dd>インデックス化されたデータベースへ非同期的にアクセスするための機構を、アプリケーションへ提供する、&nbsp;<a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/IDBFactory\"><code>IDBFactory</code></a> オブジェクトです。</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"例","title":"例","isH3":false,"content":"<p>次のコードはデータベースを非同期に開くリクエストを生成しています。データベースが開かれた後、リクエストの onsuccess ハンドラーが呼ばれます。:</p>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js;highlight:[3] notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> db<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">openDB</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n <span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> DBOpenRequest <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> window<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>indexedDB<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">open</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"toDoList\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n DBOpenRequest<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function-variable function\">onsuccess</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">e</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n   db <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> DBOpenRequest<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>result<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"仕様","title":"仕様","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Specification</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Status</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Comment</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/IndexedDB/#idl-def-IDBEnvironment\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Indexed Database API 2.0<br><small lang=\"ja\">IDBEnvironment の定義</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-rec\">勧告</span></td>\n   <td>&nbsp;</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"ブラウザ実装状況","id":"browser_compatibility","isH3":false,"data":null,"query":"api.IDBEnvironment","browsers":null}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect3\">\n<p></p><p></p>\n</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"関連情報","title":"関連情報","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/IndexedDB_API/Using_IndexedDB\">IndexedDBの使用</a></li>\n <li>トランザクションの開始: <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/IDBDatabase\"><code>IDBDatabase</code></a></li>\n <li>トランザクションの使用: <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/IDBTransaction\"><code>IDBTransaction</code></a></li>\n <li>キーの範囲の設定: <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/IDBKeyRange\"><code>IDBKeyRange</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n <li>データの取り出しと変更: <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/IDBObjectStore\"><code>IDBObjectStore</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n <li>カーソルの使用: <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/IDBCursor\"><code>IDBCursor</code></a></li>\n <li>参考例: <a class=\"external\" href=\"https://github.com/mdn/to-do-notifications/tree/gh-pages\" rel=\" noopener\">To-do Notifications</a> (<a class=\"external\" href=\"https://mdn.github.io/to-do-notifications/\" rel=\" noopener\">view example live</a>.)</li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"プロパティ","id":"プロパティ"},{"text":"例","id":"例"},{"text":"仕様","id":"仕様"},{"text":"ブラウザ実装状況","id":"browser_compatibility"},{"text":"関連情報","id":"関連情報"}],"summary":"IndexedDB API の IDBEnvironment インタフェースには、IndexedDB の機能へアクセスするための indexedDB プロパティがあります。これは、window と Workerオブジェクトによって実装された、最上位の IndexedDB インタフェースです。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"IDBEnvironment","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"IDBEnvironment","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"ja/web/api/idbenvironment","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/ja/web/api/idbenvironment/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web","title":"開発者向けのウェブ技術"},{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web/API","title":"Web API"},{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web/API/IDBEnvironment","title":"IDBEnvironment"}],"pageTitle":"IDBEnvironment - Web API | MDN","noIndexing":false}}